216
00:39:07,630 --> 00:39:11,230
And I'd like to talk a little bit
more about the gene enrichment, but

217
00:39:11,230 --> 00:39:12,790
I think that work is
actually still ongoing.

218
00:39:13,090 --> 00:39:17,650
What you see is that there does appear
to be an enrichment for cellular

219
00:39:17,650 --> 00:39:21,830
sensory kind of things and
olfactory receptor genes.

220
00:39:23,540 --> 00:39:25,280
So what's going on?

221
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:28,780
Why is this phenomenon very ubiquitous?

222
00:39:28,860 --> 00:39:29,900
It must be maintained somehow.

223
00:39:30,800 --> 00:39:32,260
I think it's important to consider

